High-frequency wordlist reading
========================================================
```{r echo=FALSE}
# HF word-reading
score <- df$El.ord.Rigtige.10sek
ggplot(df, aes(Farve, score, fill = Farve, message= FALSE, warnings = FALSE)) +
  stat_summary(fun.data = min.mean.sd.max, geom = "boxplot", na.rm=TRUE)  +
  geom_jitter(position = position_jitter(width=.1), size=2, na.rm=TRUE) + 
  ggtitle("Højfrekvente ord (Elbros ordlist korrekt/10 sec)") +
  xlab("Gruppe") +
  scale_fill_manual(name = "X", values = c("white", "green", "yellow", "red"), guide = FALSE) +
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(1, 11))



```
